{
  "stem": "24814.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The-- these men were crawling out through the mud on their hands and knees, kissing the gas cans on scout cars and fell dead.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "At least they knew they'd been liberated, whatever good that did them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So we came around the corner, and then we heard a few shots.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we thought, uh-oh.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Our [INAUDIBLE] carbine, because there were always SS snipers hiding in the woods and things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we came around the corner, and there was the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Big barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they had a mob of people, and an American officer standing there, shooting his pistol in the air.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the people were-- it looked bizarre.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were falling, they were lying, they were hanging onto each other, they were so weak, that-- some could stand, some were lying in the mud.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It kind of resolved itself as we came up, this inchoate form, into a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they saw us come in with that Jeep full of loaves of bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Well, it turned out the officer was from the American Allied military government.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And his [LAUGHS] idea was he was getting their attention by shooting his pistol in the air, while he tried to get their names and addresses on a piece of paper on a clipboard, which is about the mentality of the Allied military government at that stage.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Of all the useless procedures I could imagine, that was the last one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But there he was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were trying to cooperate, poor people, because he was an American.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They loved him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were falling in the mud, and he's saying, what's your name?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where do you live?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] They saw that food, and they-- forget the military government.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They came for us, hundreds of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
